{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d045cf98e0","title":"关于部队支左的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"40b3962d6b","index":0,"year":1967,"month":4,"day":null,"articleId":"d045cf98e0"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"70a1e48626","name":"军队支左","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji49","name":"毛泽东全集第49卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/49-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji49":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"91d8b3f7fe","type":"title","text":"关于部队支左的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"d045cf98e0"},{"id":"039d21a249","type":"paragraph","text":"军队的威信必须坚决维护，不能有半点含糊。拥军爱民社论的发表是当前工作的中心。军队第一次支左、支工、支农、军训、军管是大规模的战斗任务，犯错误是难免的，问题在于当前主要危险是有人把解放军打下去。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"d045cf98e0"},{"id":"1cec96222a","type":"paragraph","text":"支左支错，支到保守派方向去，改过来就行了，允许的嘛。我们在这五大工作中，三分之二做对了，三分之一做错了，就是很好了。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"d045cf98e0"},{"id":"ab21dc369c","type":"paragraph","text":"有的受老婆孩子观点的影响，有的是县委书记或地委书记，他们的孩子是那个地方的保守派，或者是老婆是那个地方当权派之一，这是值得我们警惕的。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"d045cf98e0"}],"page":{"id":"3e305e75cb","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"d045cf98e0","start":426,"end":426}}}},"__N_SSG":true}